      "code": "# Define normalization: remove diacritics, tatweel, punctuation; unify hamza; lowercase; collapse spaces.\nimport re\narabic_diacritics = re.compile(r'[\\u0610-\\u061A\\u064B-\\u065F\\u06D6-\\u06ED]')\ntatweel = re.compile(r'\\u0640')\n\ndef normalize_ar(s):\n    if s is None:\n        return \"\"\n    s = str(s)\n    # remove diacritics and tatweel\n    s = arabic_diacritics.sub('', s)\n    s = tatweel.sub('', s)\n    # unify hamza forms\n    s = s.replace('أ','ا').replace('إ','ا').replace('آ','ا').replace('ؤ','و').replace('ئ','ي').replace('ة','ه').replace('ى','ي')\n    # remove punctuation and non-letters/digits/spaces\n    s = re.sub(r'[^\\u0600-\\u06FF0-9\\s]', ' ', s)\n    # lowercase (not necessary for Arabic)\n    s = s.lower()\n    # collapse spaces\n    s = re.sub(r'\\s+', ' ', s).strip()\n    return s\n\ndef char_lcs(a,b):\n    # compute length of LCS for characters\n    m, n = len(a), len(b)\n    dp = [0]*(n+1)\n    for i in range(m):\n        prev = 0\n        for j in range(n):\n            tmp = dp[j+1]\n            if a[i]==b[j]:\n                dp[j+1] = prev+1\n            else:\n                dp[j+1] = max(dp[j+1], dp[j])\n            prev = tmp\n    return dp[n]\n\ndef similarity(a,b):\n    # normalized LCS as 2*LCS/(len(a)+len(b))\n    if not a or not b:\n        return 0.0\n    lcs = char_lcs(a,b)\n    return 2*lcs / (len(a)+len(b))\n\noriginal_span_full = \"وَلَا تَرْتَعوا بِقُلُوبِكُمُ الْعَنَاتِ أَن تَكُونُوا شَاهِدِينَ عَلَى أَيّامِ اللَّهِ وَتَرْجُمُونَ قَومًا وَتُصْلِحُونَ\"\nprovided_snippet = \"وَلَا تَرْ...ُصْلِحُونَ\"\nnorm_full = normalize_ar(original_span_full)\nnorm_full",
